title: Bring Doom Bots back
body: It was so fun! It was a short little game everyone enjoyed. BRING IT BACK!

replies.body:
According to the [Teemoing 2016 Page](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/skins/the-teemoing-2016), it's scheduled to come back on the 28th, two days from now.

Let me know if you have any other questions. ^.^
